OL,5, Fraudsters who scammed pensioners out  
OL,6, of #200,000 by claiming to be police   
OL,7, officers have been jailed.             
OL,9,FThe four contacted victims by telephone
OL,10,Fand told them their bank accounts had  
OL,11,Fbeen targeted.                         
